Ranger Help for: skilltree
==========================

SYNTAX:      skilltree (or: tree)
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
Shows the complete Ranger skill tree organized by branch: Survival,
Cartography, Hunting, Husbandry, Attack, and Archery.

Each skill is marked with its status:
  [*] = learned (ready to use)
  [ ] = available to learn (prerequisites met)
  [-] = locked (prerequisites not yet met)

The tree also shows slot costs and prerequisite skills for each entry.
Use this to plan which skills to learn next.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: learn, slots, skills, advancement
